    ('13', '.COM domain search enhancements', 'This project supports both the "domain unification" and the core .COM search enhancements efforts. The key aspects are to: 1) create an "entity-level" search; 2) create an index of "search suggestions"; 3) add new content from the /corporate website, and support their search experience alongside of .COM core''s.聽In later iteration will we address 4) add functionality to Document Search that will support the UX needs of the .COM Search Results page..', -1, 5, 2, '#1954a0', '2019-05-30T00:00:00', '2019-07-10T00:00:00', null, 'Cloud - Jun-Jul 2019', '2019-05-30T00:00:00', '2019-07-10T00:00:00', 47, 47, null, null, 'SRCH-2459'),
