    ('51', 'Direct 3x Morningstar Select Retirement', 'JTBD: When I visit The Equity/Credit section of Direct 3x, I want to traverse to Cloud Research Portal so I can still access Morningstar''s analyst research.聽聽Background:聽Tickets aligning to this CLP epic are to meet the Morningstar Select Retirement timeline of December 14th 2019. Implementation of this ticket will aid in our objective to achieve 5,000 monthly active users on the Cloud platform by EOY.聽PitchBook will be the primary and Premium, Morningstar Analyst Buyside Equity Research platform. Research Portal will be the secondary option where a subset of the Equity research content will live-on for existing Direct 3x users to access.聽', 399, 5, 5, '#046895', null, null, null, 'Cloud - Oct - Nov 2019', '2019-10-03T00:00:00', '2019-11-13T00:00:00', 7, 7, null, null, 'CLP-1091'),
    ('52', 'Integrate Research Portal in Advisor Workstation On Prem Server Requests and Buildout', 'Continued from -CLP-455- for commercial PM planning and prioritization, context can be found here: https://msjira.morningstar.com/browse/AWSE-25696 * Updated Gap analysis from ARC/Cloud for content parity * Identify RPS content collections * UX design * Visual design * Edition content definition (on cloud and in our service this is called "Persona") * EAMS JWT (depending on timing)', 508, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 3, 3, null, null, 'CLP-803'),
