    ('140', 'Retiring GSA Content Search for PHX Sites', 'The .COM PHX site uses a Google Search Appliance to search for documents and video content across the site. The contract is up in July 2018; they want to replace the functionality with MDR Search''s document capabilities. The .CA, .AU, and .UK sites will continue using the MDR Search for their document/content searching, and adjustments made to the PHX solution will need to encompass all four sites in terms of scope/impact. For the first phase, the documents will be housed in RPS; for the second, after PHX gets authoring in AEM stood up, we will have documents loaded in by the PHX team from AEM. Goal is to have testable version up by January 2018, so that we have 5-6 months of testing and reconfiguration to work with.', -1, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, 'PI0', '2019-05-01T00:00:00', '2019-05-31T00:00:00', 29, 29, null, null, 'SRCH-1300'),
