    ('152', 'To Move Smart Search To SOLR Cloud 5', 'From Yikui:About smart search, there is potential live issue.https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/PDS/2014-02-21+Smart+Search%3A+Solr+lost+response+for+any+update+request+in+SolrCloudhttps://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/PDS/2015-01-09+Smart+search+Solr+cloud+on+pssmrtsrch61+stop+responsingSimilar issue for News solr cloud:https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/PDS/2014-07-09+News+solr+on+adsearch84+stop+responding%2C+index+update+delaySo I suggest that we could only update Solr to 5.x on the existing production environment.', -1, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, 'PI0', '2019-05-01T00:00:00', '2019-05-31T00:00:00', 0, 0, null, null, 'SRCH-801'),
