    ('158', 'To Move News Search To SOLR Cloud 5', 'So far we are facing couple of challenges1. Increment of index stops with no reason2. Search also stops working3. Resilience/Fault tolerance not there. SPOF (Single Point Of Failure) causes all failure.4. Recover of Index&Search is not quick5. Avoid full index as it cause overhead.6. Services affected (News Search, Smart Search, Tasks & Notes)7. Notification is not reliableIn order to solve these challenges and pains, we need to move to SOLR Cloud. At the first stage, we will move News Search to SOLR Cloud 5', -1, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, 'PI0', '2019-05-01T00:00:00', '2019-05-31T00:00:00', 68, 68, null, null, 'SRCH-701'),
