    ('165', 'Solr cloud stability', 'The current solr cloud is not stable.We need to try new version to Solr to see if Solr has improved the stability of Solr cloud.RCA:https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/PDS/2014-07-09+News+solr+on+adsearch84+stop+responding%2C+index+update+delayhttps://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/PDS/2015-01-09+Smart+search+Solr+cloud+on+pssmrtsrch61+stop+responsing', -1, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, 'PI0', '2019-05-01T00:00:00', '2019-05-31T00:00:00', 4, 4, null, null, 'SRCH-642'),
