    ('167', 'Retire custom search service', '*Ready to retired:*QS id service: IDS4QSQTQS screener: Screener4QSQT Screener for Credit SuisseField FinderInvestment finder The work for the retirement is: 1)	Document the steps: remove monitor, stop production, stop service, remove service, decommission servers etc鈥?)	Double check there is no live product traffic to the services (exclude the monitoring)3)	Submit requests to network team.Tech team, add anything necessary.', -1, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, 'PI0', '2019-05-01T00:00:00', '2019-05-31T00:00:00', 0, 0, null, null, 'SRCH-581'),
