    ('170', 'Mercer Project', '*General* * Morningstar is exploring a partnership with a third party (Mercer) who would allow us to consume/display their strategy database and research in Cloud * Mornignstar has strategies in our existing databases that we''d like to also surface and function in Cloud * Performance related components', 110, 5, 2, null, '2019-05-30T00:00:00', '2019-07-10T00:00:00', null, 'Cloud - Jun-Jul 2019', '2019-05-30T00:00:00', '2019-07-10T00:00:00', 31, 31, '11', 'Release Mercer Performance, Operations, and Portfolio Data in Cloud', 'RSMR-3736'),
