    ('186', 'Personal Finance Management real time service', 'Project: Personal Financial Management (PFM)Scope:聽On demand PFM data flowDependencies: Transaction Classifier in BAA, Non-Investment Data ImportNon-investment transactional data will be imported from BAA and delivered to Data API v2 for PFM calculations to create income, expenses, savings and budget data which will then be surfaced in the PFM components. This will happen overnight for batched data and on demand for daily updates.Data Flow:BAA > Import > Data API v2 > PFM componentsDetailed diagram:聽[https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/SWDO/PFM+Architecture]聽On demand data flow is needed for: # Repeat users who need the daily delta of new transactions:聽[https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/SWDO/On+Demand+Update+Import+PFM] # First time account addition which need all historical data:聽[https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/SWDO/New+Account+Update+Import+PFM]聽PFM components will be integrated in Client Web Portal for clients of Office advisors and sold as standalone EC components for institutional clients.', 619, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'CLP-1094'),
