    ('193', 'Create Right Captical Integration Card in Office', 'As an Office User, I would like to see a new integration Card in Office for RightCapital so I can view their information and revoke their access.AC 1. Title of the card is "RightCapital", one string with no space.AC 1.1 embed URL for RightCapital''s login webpage: [https://www.rightcapital.com/login]AC 2. Display RightCapital''s company description in the card.聽 text copy = "RightCapital provides web-based innovative financial planning software solutions."AC 3. Display RightCapital''s Tool capability in the question mark pop-up.聽 text copy = "With the integration, you can view Morningstar Office Cloud client and account position data directly in your third party tool.聽 Please contact RightCapital support for help with enabling the integration."AC 4. Display RightCapital''s support information in the pop-up. ph and email info = "Ph: (888) 982-9596, opt. 2" "Email: support@rightcapital.com"AC 5. "Access Code" text and functionality should not be displayed.聽 Right Capital will be integrated with UIM''s Oauth 2.0.AC 6. The "Active" indicator should be displayed if user is connected to RightCapital.AC 6.1 Using UIM API to check if user is connected to RightCapital:[https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/PDS/UIM+API+Resource+Descriptions:|https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/PDS/UIM+API+Resource+Descriptions][/sso/oauth2/\{realm}/\{guid}/applications|#UIMAPIResourceDescriptions-/sso/oauth2/][GET -聽Gets the client (application) integrations for the resource owner|https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/PDS/UIM+API+Resource+Descriptions#UIMAPIResourceDescriptions-GET-Getstheclient(application)integrationsfortheresourceowner]AC 7. A "Remove Access" option should be displayed If user is connected to RightCapital.AC 7.1. When "Remove Access" is selected, we should use UIM API to revoke RightCapital''s access to the user''s account and the "Active" indicator should disappear:[https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/PDS/UIM+API+Resource+Descriptions][/sso/oauth2/\{realm}/\{guid}/applications/\{clientId}|#UIMAPIResourceDescriptions-/sso/oauth2/][DELETE -聽Deletes the client integration for the resource owner|https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/PDS/UIM+API+Resource+Descriptions#UIMAPIResourceDescriptions-DELETE-Deletestheclientintegrationfortheresourceowner]聽AC 8. Add the following text copy at the bottom of the card:鈥淭o set up integration with RightCapital, please login to RightCapital at [https://www.rightcapital.com/login], navigate to the *INTGRATIONS* page, select Morningstar from the Integration partners list, and follow the instructions displayed.鈥?,Feature"', 38, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 4, 4, '79', 'Office Cloud - Report Sharing Integration', 'CLP-1021'),
