    ('241', 'Modernizing Grid/Screener', 'The base code for Grid/Screener was built many years ago.聽 It uses outdated technology that makes it hard to develop reliable, bug free, testable components.聽 We have refactored some code by switching to Base Grid, and redoing the Create List/Add Investment/Locate popover, and we are in the process of upgrading the Peer Analytics panel from Backbone to Vue.js.聽 But we need to make an investment in modernizing the rest in order for this to be sustainable.聽 This includes: * Upgrading Screener to Vue.js * Upgrading Column Set Management to Vue.js * Upgrading Scorecard Modal to Vue.js * Re-platforming our data service layer.聽 Options include: ** .NET Core ** Node.js * Fixing how our component is rendered, specifically for different browser window sizes, resizing, and zooming * Improving how sub components communicate with each other * Deleting unused code * Improving test coverage聽聽', 570, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'GCS-1304'),
