    ('267', 'Account Aggregation MVP [Q2 2019]', 'Review and refine user flow, visuals, and聽interactions for production-fidelity account aggregation prototype, including coding refinements. Included in this flow are: # Account Addition # Account List # Account Edit to resolve connection issues*What do users need most right now?* * Be oriented in the聽flow and understand what they are about to do/currently聽doing * Trust the system as they are sharing personal credentials to financial institutions * Have a high level understanding of their net worth * Identify accounts with connection issues and have聽a resolution path when they encounter issues*What''s critical?*聽 * Users should have visibility of system status * Identify bumpers to keep users on the happy path and develop accompanying UI ** Goal is to encourage users to aggregate all of their accounts * When errors are encountered there should be a clear path to resolution*How does this fit into the service?* * Onboards the user * Creates a personalized net worth view * Is a prerequisite for the PFM workflow', -1, 5, 2, '#F0A509', '2019-04-01T00:00:00', '2019-06-30T00:00:00', null, 'Financial Planning - Q2 2019', '2019-04-01T00:00:00', '2019-06-30T00:00:00', 31, 31, '55', 'CWP: Personal Financial Management (PFM) MVP', 'CP-1324'),
