    ('348', 'Fiserv Sleeve Data Integration', 'Scope # Analyze Fiserv''s sleeve data files聽 鈥?Done and find the Performance Gap between the Fiserv and聽 Office # Create database schema聽 鈥?Done # Create ETL聽 聽 聽 聽 聽 聽 聽 聽 聽 聽 聽 聽 鈥?Done # Test ETL with sample data聽 鈥?Done-------------------------- Fiserv will聽send the daily holding/Performance/Transaction data of Sleeve accounts to Morningstar FTP.聽 Need set a job to move those data to S3 Bucket.聽 * Once data arrive S3 basket, triage a real-time ETL, save the update to Amazon DynamoDB, it will have the last snapshot data for Web Side.聽 * On schedule time, run daily ETL job, save the聽cumulative update to data warehouse DB, it will have all the historical data for the Daily AUM report.聽聽', -1, 2, 5, null, null, null, null, 'Managed Portfolios - Q3 2019', '2019-07-01T00:00:00', '2019-09-30T00:00:00', 11, 11, '29', 'UMA (Multi-strategies) MVP', 'MPUMA-70'),
    ('349', 'Direct Cloud Integration Analysis', 'Objective* A documented approach on how to use current Direct Cloud feature to execute model CRUD* Decide if either Investment Management Team or Investment Operations team will use the proposed approachData analysis* Import/create one MIS model to Direct Cloud as Model Portfolio* Import/create same MIS model to Direct Cloud as Client Account* Import/create custom benchmark associated with the same MIS model* Determine data differences for performance, risk, asset allocation, and portfolio analyticsDirect Cloud Login* URL: https://direct.morningstar.com/framework/login?redirectUrl=/framework/* Username: PM1.DWM@morningstar.com* Password pm1!DWM@', -1, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'MPUMA-3'),
