    ('371', 'Automate MR Translation Process', '*Background*:聽Currently, the 7-page GFR is being translated manually via email with agencies, but this process will eventually be retired from lack of demand. There''s interest in translating one-pagers. There''s a client that needs Japanese translations.The Research Products/Distributions team needs to automate the translation of GFRs for a one-page report. # GFR collections (US, EMEA , AUS) # Translate 2 fields only: Deck (overall), Analysis (within the same child doc ID preferably) # Automated process similar to equity process where RMs can set up coverage based on fund ID or share class ID of the fund. # Set up the initial process and testing with Peter & Clark聽+Ewa''s answers to questions via email 12/11/2018+: # Is there a report team who will need to consume and test this translated report? Does the report already exist or is there a target date? Who is the contact for this report team? ## Answer:聽That will go into MFB report, attached here, which is produced by MPS team, it is likely to be coordinated by Girjinder Vithal鈥檚 team ( MPS ops team), and the product managers are: Corin Burton for EMEA and Kelly Barnes in the US. ## Attached MFB PDF example:[^RPS-3381 MFB.pdf] # Is this going to show up in a digital format too? You mentioned the M* page. ## Answer: Not sure I am clear on what do you mean by 鈥榙igital format鈥? can you elaborate please? # Is there a need for a preview to prevent cut off text? If so, the report team needs to build this for RPS. ## Answer: No need for RPS preview, as we will just work with report team to establish how the template will need to be adjusted to fit the translated content # Is there someone who can coordinate with P&C? ## Answer: That will be Kelly 馃槉 # Is there a contract now? When will a client need this? ## Answer: Contract is in progress (will probably sign in the next 2 weeks) for Japanese translations, and client will likely need it by end of Q1, but we also now have another prospect who is interested in other languages as well, so it will be great if we can automate process in the next few months.+STG Test Doc Created and Launched without issues 12.17/2018+:Japanese analysis text translation and deck added only:[http://rps-stg.morningstar.com/api/v2/140543541/Documents/902275?fields=Id,colid,colname,publishdate,content]!image-2018-12-17-11-23-21-318.png!聽聽', -1, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'RPS-3381'),
