    ('388', 'RPS QuickBase Integration', 'RPS and Quick base needs to be in Sync for the GFR committees , voting etc to work successfully.As of now following two features needs to synced/integrated .1. File and Attachments for GFRs 2. GFR Ratings gatekeeping checkThis Epic will track tickets pertaining to these two features.聽聽+Caroline Notes 4/3+: # QB API (Patrick) ** Token to access API ** Token to service account ([RPSTechSupport@m*.com|mailto:RPSTechSupport@m*.com]) ** Token reflects read-only ** QB Table ID: *big8wkr5y* ** Data Schema: _See聽----DBOPS-11305---- for_ [~edeleoz]_''s recommendation on DB storage._ ### Fund ID (unique key)*:* ETFs mapped to OE fund ID is appended with an E (11 varchar) ### UnresolvedProposal (0 zero = good to go OR record ID (numeric) OR NULL) ### Committee Approved Overall DB Trans (NULL or RPS DB values) ### Committee Approved People DB Trans (NULL or RPS DB聽values) ### Committee Approved Performance DB Trans (NULL or RPS DB聽values) ### Committee Approved Price DB Trans (NULL or RPS DB聽values) ### Committee Approved Process DB Trans (NULL or RPS DB聽values) ### Record ID# - Most Recent Complete Ratings Meeting - Complete Date (UTC) *  **  *** Unresolved (create new DP in table) **** Captures following statuses: working, ready, in review, deferred, expired = Record ID **** Completed = (no Record ID in QB related to the fund with status of working, ready, in review, deferred or expired) *** MostRecentCommitteeApproved **** Always populated if previously rated **** NULL = RPS unset **** NA = example, Price pillar SMA doesn鈥檛 apply ** QB statuses and Descriptions *** Working 鈥?proposal hasn鈥檛 submitted *** Ready 鈥?proposal submitted (committee is free to review it) *** In Review 鈥?formally started (triggered by voter recording a vote) *** Completed 鈥?finalized by committee (valid ratings) **** QB will populate ratings in MostRecentCommitteeApproved *** Cancelled 鈥?indicate ignore the proposal *** Deferred 鈥?descent *** Expired 鈥?didn鈥檛 complete in time # RPS-QB Communication ** Scenario 3 NULL completed ratings, rec ID (initiation) ### analyst starts document, RPS shows unset ratings, proposal in progress, RPS shows message with QB rec ID ### "Ratings not finalized. See rec ID <number>. (hyperlinked URL to QB record) ### _Note_: UI show unset whereas DB = 0 (zero) ** Scenario 2 completed ratings previous, rec ID ### analyst starts document, -RPS pulls in previous ratings-, -proposal in progress, RPS shows message with QB rec ID- ### -"Ratings not finalized. See rec ID <number>. (hyperlinked URL to QB record)- ### MAR requirement = final ratings approval date & time ** Scenario 1 completed ratings, nothing in unresolved (no issues in RPS) ### analyst free to write and set ready and launch ### MAR requirement = final ratings approval date & time ** Scenario 4 NULL completed ratings, no rec ID ### analyst starts document, RPS shows unset ratings, RPS shows message without QB rec ID ### "No ratings available." # UI Workflow (business rules and user messages) # R', -1, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 82, 82, null, null, 'RPS-2444'),
