    ('415', 'Post Tax returns for UK', '+Background :+聽One of the feedback items from Direct cloud training聽 in UK was the ability to view UK post tax returns.聽Currently in 3.x there is a Setting for Return/Price type which has the option of choosing "Mixed" . The Mixed options allows for UK funds to show Post tax returns without having to change at individual Dp''s.聽聽UK team is requesting for similar setting/functionality in direct cloud and it''s a showstopper features for users who''re willing to be on boarded to Direct cloud.聽+Business Use case :+聽 * UK clients would like to view returns & MPT Dp''s after tax adjusted as default where applicable.聽 * 聽Allowing SAL to be able to switch to DATA API v2 from RDB for currency converted post tax data. The switch will in turn support European retail sites to switch to SAL from EC. (聽PPI-4329) * Support Z score option on Post tax returns for UK clients (PPI-3312) * Support EC teams to switch over to API v2聽We need coordination across multiple teams to add this feature into Direct cloud and also the work will extend beyond a single program planning cycle.聽 I divided the work into phase and this +CLP is for phase 1 only.+聽聽For Mar - Apr program planning cycle we plan on working on phase1 and below is the scope.聽+Scope of Phase 1+In phase 1 only Security squad & Framework teams are involved. Framework team will added a mixed return setting option in global settings and security squad will start working on sourcing post tax return Index data to surface post tax data for聽 * Total Returns聽 * Market Returns聽 * Primary Returns聽聽聽聽+Below is a screenshot of setting in 3.x+聽聽聽 !image-2019-02-13-10-47-59-295.png!聽+Setting to be added in Direct Cloud ( for representation purpose only)+聽聽 !image-2019-02-22-11-24-29-141.png!聽聽聽聽聽+Details of聽Data sourcing required+聽 # Source Tax adjusted data from TSDB for TS types : 1,15,16,119 # Populate PRI tables # Populate Most recent tables聽+API changes+聽 # API enhancement required to read mixed return setting from global settings and check if RI data exists for Tax adjusted use that for return calculation and if tax adjusted data is missing then use Pre tax data.聽 # The return types will still remain same which are total/market/Gross/Primary for dynamic calc and Load Adjusted return added additionally for base currency聽*Open questions*聽 * How do we clean up the option of Post Tax 鈥?Pre Liquidation and Post Liquidation option for Non US funds. The concept doesn鈥檛 really apply for non US funds.聽Detailed list of task by squad to complete the聽 work.聽Teams Involved.聽 * Direct cloud Framework team聽 * GCS team聽 * Data API v2 - Security API聽聽聽Work required in Sequence order # Confirm all Dp''s which are applicable for UK post tax . So far I identified NAV and Returns (Market, Total, Gross, Primary) based on the data availability聽 # Security API team to source from TSDB and store in mart.聽 # For base currency clean up meta keys to not show post tax data under return type: Post Tax - Post Liquidation. Currently post tax data for U', 652, 5, 2, null, '2019-05-30T00:00:00', '2019-07-10T00:00:00', null, 'Cloud - Jun-Jul 2019', '2019-05-30T00:00:00', '2019-07-10T00:00:00', 5, 5, null, null, 'CLP-1071'),
