    ('550', 'WFE-4285', 'WHen the owner of an IRA dies, there are a myriad of rules that the beneficiary must follow in order to inherit the IRA. Beneficiaries can be Spouses, Non-Spouses, or a Trust.WFE currently does not model inherited IRA rules explicitly; some options are partially modeled but need some attention. The purpose of this ticket is to describe what needs to be done to model inherited IRAs.For purposes of this Story, we will limit the scope to Inherited IRAs from Non-Spouses.http://www.schwab.com/public/schwab/investing/retirement_and_planning/understanding_iras/inherited_ira/withdrawal_rules', -1, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'WFE-3655'),
