    ('553', 'BATCH', 'Request originates from TRP who want the ability to run batches of WFE cases.Instead of making 10,000 calls to the WFE web-service, client will send a batch file with 10,000 files in it, and we would then handle all of that on our side.聽 Then at the end, we鈥檇 send back a package of 10,000 outputs. Max user count is 2.2 million, although T Rowe will not send everything at once, more likely is a staggering through the month of plans being sent in smaller batches.This Epic is to track the development work required to establish the back-end operational requirements.Also need to work with聽TRP to establish how they want to pass the input files to us and how we''ll pass the results back. * FTP/SFTP * T Rowe will create an alert for notification - creating a notification process is therefore not in scope for this first iteration聽', -1, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'WFE-3411'),
