    ('556', 'Empower- CAS Migration Q&A', 'This epic is meant to store the Q&A between Morningstar and Empower regarding their migration to, and usage of CAS. Underlying tickets are meant to serve as reference for how Morningstar has communicated to Empower how to use select engine functionality.聽Project Definition:聽 聽 Empower is migrating from TAS to CAS, building their own Managed Accounts workflow and UI.聽 Empower will offer institutioanl (traditional) Managed Accounts solution, as well as an Advisor Managed Accounts solution.聽 Initial intention is for Empower to launch, phase 1, using WFE version 4.30.xx, without annuity advice, in order to mirror existing TAS deployment.聽 After comfort with launch results using 4.30, Empower would upgrade to a more recent WFE version including enhanced annuity advice.聽Estimated Timelines: * Q3 2018 = Phase 1 launch * Q1 2019 = annuity availability聽Related Client Wiki聽page:聽 [https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/MIMTECH/Empower+%28Great+West%29+-+CAS+deployment]聽', -1, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'WFE-3288'),
