    ('559', 'Project WIMP', 'Stand up CAS on AWS. This will be created as a separate instance on AWS for each client. It will be a streamlined set up, as CAS will be calling the WFE web-service on AWS instead of a client needing to host several servers to enable WFE.Eventually when APC is fully stood up on AWS as well, everything can be linked together.Use PostgreSQL for DB needs. Audit Log can be written here or moved to S3 data storage.聽', -1, 2, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 2, 2, null, null, 'WFE-2979'),
    ('560', 'Inherited IRAs', 'WHen the owner of an IRA dies, there are a myriad of rules that the beneficiary must follow in order to inherit the IRA.   Beneficiaries can be Spouses, Non-Spouses, or a Trust.  WFE currently does not model inherited IRA rules explicitly; some options are partially modeled but need some attention.   The purpose of this ticket is to describe what needs to be done to model inherited IRAs.For purposes of this Story, we will limit the scope to Inherited IRAs for Spouses.http://www.schwab.com/public/schwab/investing/retirement_and_planning/understanding_iras/inherited_ira/withdrawal_rules', -1, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'WFE-2954'),
