    ('571', 'Total Wealth Enhancements [2019 Q3]', 'The calculation of Human Capital currently considers the following: * Future Savings * Social Security Benefits * DB Pension BenefitsWe propose to add the following income sources * Immediate Fixed Annuities * Immediate Variable Annuities * Guaranteed Withdrawal AnnuitiesWe also plan to modify the asset allocation assumptions for DB Pension benefits*As Pension (DB) and IFA were merged into 4.46 prior to refactoring work, these will be released in 4.46 but the Short Circuit work means they are not operational until such time as we have all Total Wealth work completed.*2019 10 14 - Jay Mitchell - The subject was "Include Additional and/or Modify Existing Guaranteed Income Sources for the HC calculation". I changed it to Total Wealth Enhancements [2019 Q3]聽', -1, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 27, 27, null, null, 'WFE-1735'),
