    ('578', 'Paperless Statements Auto Enrollment', 'h1. BackgroundCompliance changed the IMA to allow for us to auto enroll users in paperless statements back in November 2018.聽 Compliance wants to auto enroll people in paperless statements as it will save thousands of $$$ per year on mailing paper statements.聽Notes from meeting with Charity and Sara on 4/11: * We will be in charge of collecting the email address and saving to a location (to be determined by Charity) only * Need Charity to confirm the following ** whether we need to collect joint owner email address ** where to save email addresses in the db to kick off their side of things聽聽', -1, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 32, 0, null, null, 'MISLEGACY-4924'),
