    ('581', 'Fidelity Ops Tool', 'h1. BackgroundTo be able to request and maintain the Wealthscape IDs and G numbers required to gain access to Fidelity''s tools, we need to build out a tool that will be used by the sales/service/ops teams to request WS IDs and G numbers.聽 This tool will need to accommodate a number of different situations.h1. ScopeWe will accommodate a few different situations: * Advisor moving to Fidelity from non-Fidelity ** Request G number (if not already assigned) and Wealthscape ID * Advisor moving to non-Fidelity from Fidelity ** Delete G number and leave Wealthscape ID active * Advisor moving to Fidelity from non-Fidelity (has already worked with Fidelity at some point in the past) ** Request G number (if not already assigned) only聽', -1, 5, 5, '#1954a0', null, null, null, 'Managed Portfolios - Q3 2019', '2019-07-01T00:00:00', '2019-09-30T00:00:00', 13, 13, '89', 'Fidelity Online Account Opening', 'MISUPGRADE-4154'),
