    ('584', 'Dollar Cost Averaging (DCA)', 'h1. BackgroundWhen running a proposal, the advisor should have the ability to include a dollar cost averaging plan. Once entered within the proposal, we need to support the trade team''s ability to trade the account into the money market used as a holding tank for the money.聽 We also should display the dollar cost averaging information on the account once set up and active.Why would someone want to add a DCA plan?聽 Mostly because they are uncomfortable with the thought of investing all of their $$$ at once, and prefer to keep some of it ''safe'' from the market for a period of time.Here are some helpful links:[https://www.investopedia.com/terms/d/dollarcostaveraging.asp][https://www.investopedia.com/investing/dollar-cost-averaging-pays/][https://www.nerdwallet.com/blog/investing/dollar-cost-averaging-2/]h1. ScopeIncludes changes to: * proposal workflow ** The strategy selection, fees, and preview steps of the proposal process.聽 Limited to Fidelity and Schwab only. * proposal PDF ** leverage new proposal process created by red squad to surface up DCA specific data and revised IMAs * trading systems (Fiserv) ** ingest new data points to be used by trade team when trading accounts * account profile ** display active DCA on account聽聽聽', -1, 2, 5, '#046895', null, null, null, 'Managed Portfolios - Q3 2019', '2019-07-01T00:00:00', '2019-09-30T00:00:00', 154, 127, '91', 'Dollar Cost Averaging (DCA) for Brokerage', 'MISUPGRADE-4146'),
    ('585', 'DocuSign - Proposal', 'h1. BackgroundAs our users (clients and advisors) continue to become more and more focused on less paperwork/manual steps and we want to make ourselves as easy to do business with as possible, we are pushing in 2019 to make as many forms e-signature/submission compatible as possible.h1. ScopeWe will be integrating our聽proposal聽with聽Morningstar''s instance of Docusign.聽h2. About聽the聽ProposalThis document can vary in the number of pages and is required by the trade team to invest in a particular strategy.h1. Previous WorkWe did some work a few years back regarding integration of Docusign.聽 See https://msjira.morningstar.com/browse/MISUPGRADE-112聽and [https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/MISHOME/Online+Account+Opening+Project+Charter]聽for details.', -1, 5, 5, '#FF6D27', null, null, null, 'Managed Portfolios - Q3 2019', '2019-07-01T00:00:00', '2019-09-30T00:00:00', 111, 111, '143', 'DocuSign Integration', 'MISUPGRADE-4131'),
    ('586', 'DocuSign - Proprietary Forms', 'h1. BackgroundAs our clients continue to become more and more focused on less paperwork/manual steps and we want to make ourselves as easy to do business with as possible, we are pushing in 2019 to make as many forms e-signature/submission compatible as possible.h1. ScopeThe scope of this ticket is changes to the proprietary forms accessible via the forms tab on the MMP website.h1. Previous WorkWe did some work a few years back regarding integration of Docusign.聽 See https://msjira.morningstar.com/browse/MISUPGRADE-112聽and [https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/MISHOME/Online+Account+Opening+Project+Charter]聽for details.', -1, 5, 5, '#6EBDAB', null, null, null, 'Managed Portfolios - Q3 2019', '2019-07-01T00:00:00', '2019-09-30T00:00:00', 103, 87, '143', 'DocuSign Integration', 'MPZODIAC-1736'),
    ('587', 'DocuSign - Schwab Account Opening', 'h1. BackgroundAs our clients continue to become more and more focused on less paperwork/manual steps and we want to make ourselves as easy to do business with as possible, we are pushing in 2019 to make as many forms e-signature/submission compatible as possible.h1. GoalThe goal of this project is to provide the advisor and client the ability to electronically sign and submit account opening forms to Schwab via our ''Get Forms'' process.聽 Schwab allows us to use our own instance of DocuSign to sign the forms and submit them to Schwab.h1. ScopeForms accessible via our ''Get Forms'' workflow.', -1, 2, 5, '#9faebf', null, null, null, 'Managed Portfolios 2019Q4', '2019-10-01T00:00:00', '2019-12-31T00:00:00', 10, 10, '301', 'Cindy Goal 3 - Support Technology Modernization Imperative by developing new features on the TAMP to improve the advisor experience', 'MPZODIAC-1908'),
