    ('651', 'Deliver Component Visual Export to PROD', '*User Story:*聽As a user, I would like the ability to export components to visual files so I can save, communicate and investigate further*Background:*聽Visual export is one of the most common feature requests that Cloud components receive. Additionally it''s a feature gap identified for Office Cloud 2019 goals.*User Jobs:*-When I''m presenting findings and recommendations to the investment committee, I want to have both paper and digital versions of reporting materials so I can communicate effectively.-When I''m completing a review of my fund lineup, I need to export and save reports locally so I have records of my analysis聽*High level acceptance criteria:*1.) Single component at a time for export2.) Chart view and table views can be exported聽3.) PDF Export will be the output format4.) Product can customize header and footer information5.) Component settings can be displayed in the file, determined by the product teamExamples: Fund name,聽time period, benchmark, grouping, calculation setting, etc.6.)聽The export聽setting will exist in the component header, same location today as excel export', 14, 2, 5, null, null, null, null, 'Cloud - Nov-Dec 2019', '2019-11-14T00:00:00', '2019-12-25T00:00:00', 0, 0, '200', 'Component Visual Export', null),
