    ('656', '[Phase 1] - Custom calc - Returns on flink', 'h1. Phase 1聽Goal : Capture response time of API v2 requests for processing returns using Dynamic calc.h2. Products Impacted|*Product Name* |*Benefit* ||Direct web|Improve performance for sorting on Dynamic calc returns||SAL|Ability to get post tax data from API v2 to聽 draw return growth chart|聽User impact:For existing features:Direct web : * Users with saved sort on dynamic calc dp鈥檚 in their columnset will be able to view data faster in both investment and Portfolio workbooks. The exact performance numbers are yet to be determined. * Provide users with Currency conversion option for post tax returns. The feature is particularly important for Users in UK and other countries in Europe.h3. New FeaturesSAL :SAL is planning on migrating from API v1 to API v2. From SAL perspective, phase 1 is first step for API v2 to provide data and feature parity with API v1. Below are few benefits for SAL which we鈥檒l support after phase 1. * Users will be able to choose post tax with user defined currency as one of the option for return growth chart. ( PPI-4329 ).Direct web : * Users will be able to choose weekly return frequency for return calculation.Timeline : 聽Mid July.Risks:Users related : NoneTechnical : * Knowledge and working experience of Flink * Implementation of routing logic correctly * Ability to combine responses of mart and flink.聽Assumptions : * Ability for Flink to process dynamic calc returns faster than current response time.', -1, 0, 5, '#a59e89', null, null, null, 'Data Services - November-December 2019', '2019-11-06T00:00:00', '2019-12-31T00:00:00', 154, 110, '229', 'Dynamic Calc and Currency Conversion Migration Out of SQL', 'DTPA-5034'),
