    ('788', 'Cash Flow Report for Client/Account Level Objects', '*As an advisor, i would like a way to monitor & analyze聽 cash flows for my clients and their accounts so that I can keep track oh what is going on in my clients'' accounts and give them good advice.*I would benefit for cash flow analysis components in the following locations: # Client & Accounts # Presentation StudioAC1: I would like to view cash flow information for set time frames & be able to edit that time frameAC2: I would like to distinguish between incoming & outgoing transactions聽 聽 聽 聽 聽AC2.1 I would like to have a total of all聽 additions聽for the time period聽 聽 聽 聽 聽AC2.2 I would like to have a total of all withdraws for the time periodAC3: I would like the choice to聽filter by:聽 聽 聽 聽 聽AC3.1:聽Additions / Withdrawals聽 聽 聽 聽 聽AC3.2: Activity Type聽 聽 聽 聽 聽AC3.3: Security TypeAC4: I would like to view this info on both a Client aggregate level and an individual Account level_Cash Flow report for Office 3.x is attached for reference._*Other items to answer:* * What transaction types show up in cash flow reports? What is current logic in 3.x? * what are key data points when viewing cash flow info?聽 Are there dp in the 3.x report that are not needed?', 283, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'CLP-814'),
