    ('825', 'Move Cloud Equity Attribution to v2', '*Summary of Issue:*聽Cloud is still using 3.x data inputs for equity attribution because v2''s service cannot tie attribution results ti 3,x.The v2 Attribution service shares the same calculation code and logic as 3.x.聽 However, the inputs we put into the calculation service are from different sources (v2 vs. 3.x).聽We need the reference data, which is DRI and Portfolio Holdings, to be investigated and corrected in order to identify and fix the root cause.聽 Otherwise Cloud cannot fully use v2 calculation service for equity attribution.聽', 576, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'CLP-1105'),
    ('826', 'Create end-to-end monitoring for portfolio holding imports', 'We need simple monitoring to check that portfolios received by DWM are processed downstream within a reasonable amount of time.During a meeting with Dayu, Subash and Yusong we discussed setting this up at the database level. Check the number of accounts and holdings in a given import job, then confirm that those accounts and holdings are loaded in the mart after a certain time threshold (maybe start with 1 hour).If an account or holding does not appear in the mart after the defined time threshold, send an email alert to [CloudImport@morningstar.com|mailto:CloudImport@morningstar.com]聽and Data Service - Operations. Alert should include: * Import job ID * Number of accounts and holdings in import * Number of accounts and holdings in mart (this will be different & less if the alert fires)', 364, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 1, 1, null, null, 'CLP-1098'),
    ('827', 'Research Email Alerts on Followed Authors, Topics, Publications', 'Drafting the implementation ticket to capture next steps to begin implementation work for June/July聽聽JTBD: Research Topic, Publication and Author followers: When I''m monitoring a Topic, Author and/or Publication, I want to be alerted whenever Morningstar publishes any research content referencing any of the Topic, Authors or Publications that interest me聽聽聽', 698, 1, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'CLP-1095'),
    ('828', 'Import Auto Generate', 'As a BOS Import User, I want to be able to set up rules for creating recurring adjusting transactions so that we can automate a manual and repetitive process of adding the adjustments manually.聽 This will be a huge time savings opportunity for the BOS reconciliation process.', 482, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 5, 5, null, null, 'CLP-1090'),
