    ('830', 'Intentional ESG Investment List', 'JTBD: When I view my objects (lists, screens, workbooks, portfolios, clients, accounts, etc.) , I want to see a Morningstar Curated list of Intentional ESG funds, so that I can cut through the noise and access them quickly.聽AC1: A read-only list will be added into Office 3.x and Office Cloud for all users.聽AC2: The list will only contain the attached spreadsheet of securities', 514, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'CLP-1084'),
