    ('835', 'Enhance Orion > BAA > DWM integration to include householding', 'The current integration between Orion Data Services and DWM just includes client account information.聽This ticket is to expand that integration to cover householding information as well.*Overall Goal*: * When a user initiates Orion integration, not only do all their accounts become available in DWM, but also there is one new Account Groups that are automatically available: ** Client * Accounts are automatically assigned Client values during the nightly BAA feed * Users can use the Client Account Groups just like any other Account Group (they can group on these in the portfolio workbook grid, aggregated statistics show up for the account group, etc.)*Details*:To achieve this we need to: * Import Team 鈥?Add a step in the import *setup process to create the Account Group*聽for the user. This can be done via the /custom-content/data-points API or by getting impersonation rights for the user and doing it through the UI. * BAA Team 鈥?In addition to sending the export_positions file to DWM, the *export_accounts file must also be sent* * Import Team 鈥?Read data from the export_accounts file (file type: Account Profile) and load it as account groupsAn example of what is in the export_accounts file, please see an example here: [https://morningstaronline-my.sharepoint.com/:u:/r/personal/eileen_bingle_morningstar_com/Documents/Axxcess.zip?csf=1&e=0Nhx6Y]聽(it is password protected, please see eileen for access).聽*For the Client Account Group*: * Column AB & AD of the export_accounts file contain the first and last name of the client * What we want to load into the Client account group is actually the concatenation of the fields so that the account group would be, for example: "Adams, Kevin and Eileen". Concatenation would be: (FI_SUPPLIED_CLIENT_LAST,",",FI_SUPPLIED_CLIENT_FIRST) * -*Open question: Can BAA concatenate the fields into one and include a new concatenated field in the file?*-*!image-2019-05-15-14-45-01-706.png!*聽', 422, 0, 5, '#ff4e4d', null, null, null, 'Cloud_Q1 2020', '2019-12-26T00:00:00', '2020-03-18T00:00:00', 1, 1, '357', 'Placeholder-BAA Intergration to load advisor portfolio data into DWM system', 'CLP-1040'),
    ('836', 'XRay report for Office Cloud', 'As an advisor, I would like to generated the Xray report on my clients & accounts in Office Cloud so that I can include it in my quarterly reporting process. # Make the Xray report currently available in Office 3x, available to generate in Office Cloud (See attached Report)聽 # User should be able to generate report on both the Client & Account level # User should be able to generate report ad hoc ( via Client & Accounts) # User should be able to generate report via batch schedule', 101, 2, 5, '#0d2c54', null, null, null, 'Cloud - Oct - Nov 2019', '2019-10-03T00:00:00', '2019-11-13T00:00:00', 53, 48, '242', 'Office Cloud - Standard Analytical Portfolio Reports', 'CLP-1012'),
    ('837', 'POC -     POC to Enhance User experience while using Dynamic calc & Advanced Analytics', 'We want to allocate time for develop POC and identify a technology to replatform our Dyanmic calculations for returns / MPT , Peer Analytics so we can scale for more users and complex analytics.聽Below are some use cases we want to evaluate our POC to test if the Goal is met.聽聽|*Domain*聽|*Use case*|*Goal*|*Interactive/Async*|*Impacted products*聽||Grid Load|Calculate Most recent Primary returns for 50 Dp''s with 5K investments for base & non basecurrency聽 within API response time of 4 seconds|Direct cloud Grid loaded with data under 7 seconds|Interactive|Direct Cloud||Grid Load|Calculate Most recent MPT''s with Primary returns for 50 Dp''s with 5K investments for non CATcurrency聽 within API response time of 4 seconds|Direct cloud Grid loaded with data under 7 seconds|Interactive|Direct Cloud||Feed|Calculate Most recent MPT''s for 50 Dp''s of OE & ETF universe for non CATcurrency with EP ON and OFF and Standard Benchmark|Ability to generate files RiskReturnStats20_CG_FO_USA_M_20180305, Standard Benchmark_ETF & Standard Benchmark_OE.聽|Async|Olympus feeds||Feed|Calculate Most recent MPT''s for 50 Dp''s of OE & ETF universe for non CATcurrency with EP ON and OFF and Custom Benchmark聽|Ability to generate files RiskReturnStats20_CG_FO_USA_M_20180305, Standard Benchmark_ETF & Standard Benchmark_OE.聽|Async|Olympus feeds|', 631, 2, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'CLP-1003'),
