    ('847', 'Retire Office 3x Research Objects', 'Research Portal has successfully migrated all research content from the identified 3.x components and lifted engagement with Research Portal for advisor users. To save us some embarrassment with the legacy components that are no longer maintained on the home page of Office desktop, we are aiming to remove some of them and guide users to leverage the Research Portal in Office Cloud.聽Refer to tickets to be linked to this epic and the attachments for more information.聽聽The scope of this epic for the March April planning period is limited to only the following changes to Office 3.x*Home 鈥? 1) Remove the Market Commentary component 2) Remove the Morningstar Market Updates component 3) Remove the Advisor E Newsletters component 4) Remove the Manager Research component*Articles + Commentary 鈥? 1) Remove the Advisor E Newsletters component 2) Remove the Manager Research component', 712, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 1, 1, null, null, 'CLP-878'),
