    ('849', 'Managed Portfolios Account Search', 'Managed Portfolios already has epics open to enable us to integrate with Data API v2 when showing account level data on our website. However, we will also need to be able to 1) search among all Managed Portfolios accounts by search parameter, and 2) surface multiple data points for multiple accounts at one time.聽', 547, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 14, 0, null, null, 'CLP-784'),
