    ('854', 'CLP - Cloud Production Support', 'The purpose of this epic is to offer a common vehicle to track all issues flagged by the Cloud Production Support model. This epic is not聽 time-boxed and does not adhere to normal CLP prioritization rules.聽聽The Cloud Production Support model requires engineers from multiple teams to constantly monitor the platform using New Relic.聽As part of this ongoing effort, there needs to be a central place to track improvements and error elimination.[https://mswiki.morningstar.com/pages/viewpage.action?spaceKey=DIRECTPL&title=Support+Model]', 305, 2, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'CLP-692'),
