    ('869', 'CLP - License Swap or Transfer Objects', 'There are two use cases for transferring objects. 1. A user leaves the company and a period of time a new user is hired and needs to pick up the work left behind by the old user. 2. A user leaves the company and a backfill is not hired. A current user must assume the old users work. We need to transfer the users objects to a current user.The UI action will take place in the firm admin or CSC admin view in EAMS. However all components teams must be notified of the action and take responsibility for transferring a users objects. Types of Ojects:Custom SecuritiesCustom Data Points3rd Party EntitlementsListsColumn SetsWorkbooks/sheetsNotes/alertsArchived ReportsPortfolios', 325, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'CLP-106'),
    ('870', 'CLP - Future Publish Date for Notes - Q4', '*JTBD: *When I''m...* Responsible for communicating changes to the approved list  I need...* The ability to create the note today but automatically share with the larger group at a late dateSo I can... * a) Ensure that compliance guidelines are followed and the change (note) is shared with all relevant users and b) don''t need to log in on that day and manually send the note myselfTypical situation: Fund on approved list will be moved to "on hold" as of a specific date but for compliance reasons, the Home office cannot communicate that change to the field until that date', 315, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 20, 20, null, null, 'CLP-91'),
