    ('975', 'Grouping in PS for OC', 'As an Office Cloud user, I need to ability to group account holding information by one or more levels when using聽Portfolio Evaluation & Period Performance components so that I can properly customize my reports to share with my clients.聽 # Multi Level Grouping for Portfolio Evaluation & Period Performance components ## 3 Levels of Grouping ### First Level options: #### Security #### Asset Class #### Asset Class or Equity Sector #### Security Type #### Broad Asset Class #### Super Asset Class #### Account ### Second Level options: #### None #### 聽Security #### Asset Class #### Asset Class or Equity Sector #### Broad Asset Class #### Super Asset Class ##### Note: Super Asset Class is not at second level in 3.x, but we need to add that option for the Cloud version.聽聽 ### Third Level options: #### None #### 聽Security #### Asset Class #### Asset Class or Equity Sector!image-2018-09-25-11-11-48-481.png!聽聽These requirements are needed OC client Financial Planning and Info Services & to make PS at parity with the PS in 3.x聽', 78, 5, 2, null, '2019-08-22T00:00:00', '2019-10-02T00:00:00', null, 'Cloud - Aug-Sept 2019', '2019-08-22T00:00:00', '2019-10-02T00:00:00', 15, 15, '87', 'Office Cloud - Presentation Studio', 'CLP-1279'),
