    ('977', 'Intelligent content delivery through Morningstar for Advisors', 'Identify intelligent ways to push content (may it be just the articles or videos, or may be quality analysis or research from Morningstar) from our apps & device an algorithm to power it.We start small and pick easily available but less impactful content and lay the foundation for building intelligence in Morningstar for Advisors (India smartphone). This intelligence to push (recommend) most valuable & suitable content will be powered by the attributes we receive in the APIs as well as studying usage patterns.We target 鈥淢orningstar Videos鈥?for this proof of concept. The use case 鈥?鈥渞ecommend the most relevant 鈥渘ext鈥?video(s) based on the video(s) viewed by the users till now鈥? There are several usage patterns to look into for recommending the 鈥渘ext鈥?video(s):# Types of video viewed by user (depending on video category, author, etc.) [{color:#f79232}gives insight into user''s topic of choice{color}] # Videos from our list which are not viewed [{color:#f79232}display videos that user hasn鈥檛 viewed. Our objective should be to push as much Morningstar content as possible.{color}]# View count of given videos [{color:#f79232}recommend video(s) that were viewed multiple times by user 鈥?let鈥檚 call it, her/his favorites. But again, these videos are business specific, unlike FRIENDS or TWO and a HALF MEN or B.R.Chopra''s MAHABHARAT.. something we watch time and again{color}]# Number to times a video was shared [{color:#f79232}great insight, but how relevant is it for our use case! We can assume that user has already viewed the video > found it useful > and share it. So why recommend again?{color}]# Videos which are not fully viewed [{color:#f79232}We see this all the time on Netflix and Amazon Prime; but need to assess how relevant is it for our user persona and ease of implementation{color}]& more鈥e ''ll pursue 鈥渰color:#205081}*1*{color}鈥?& 鈥?{color:#205081}2{color}*鈥?to begin with.However, true intelligence is the one which I haven鈥檛 even mentioned 鈥?鈥渰color:#205081}*_Continuously listen to what user is doing 鈥?viewing videos/article, searching security, accessing clients and their portfolios, sharing IDRs, etc. and build an engine to study these activities, derive patterns and recommend most relevant & actionable content (video, article), search result, etc. through the app_*{color}鈥? This should be the strategic goal!', -1, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'MOBSOLN-33'),
