    ('1522', 'Retire Analyst Research Center from Office 3x suite of Research Objects', '*JTBD*: When I visit the Office 3.x Home Page, I want to traverse to Cloud Research Portal so I can still access Morningstar''s analyst research.聽聽*Background*:聽Tickets aligning to this CLP epic are to meet the Morningstar Analyst Research (ARC) removal requirement from Office 3x. Implementation of this ticket will aid in our objective to achieve 1,000 MAU Office Cloud users and 5,000 total monthly active users on the Cloud platform by EOY.聽Research Portal has successfully migrated all research content from the identified 3.x components and lifted engagement with Research Portal for advisor users.聽聽Web usage tracking for Analyst Research Center (ARC) via Morningstar Office, was implemented March 1, 2018. After collecting 5.5 months of data, during that period it''s estimated that 1432 unique users accessed ARC via Office 3x.聽 We are operating under this assumption since ARC''s default behavior on opening is to take a user to the Equity content then to navigate to other modules.聽|聽|Equity|Funds|ETF||OfficeUserALL|1432|587|345|The top users accessing ARC via Office 3.x include users from Morgan Stanley as the heaviest user of Equity by a huge margin, and Oppenheimer is the heaviest user of both Funds and ETF. These client''s expectations may need to be managed closely. Oppenheimer also consumes ARC content outside of the Office 3.x workflow which may mitigate any concerns.聽The scope of this epic for the August September planning period to remove ARC from Home and Articles + Commentary sections of Office 3.x*Home &gt; Analyst Research Center*聽----Office 3.x Institutional ID = 70000009-OfficeUserAll Global Equity Global Funds Global ETF Global Credit聽 (Munis was retired long ago)[https://ar.morningstar.com/membership/clienttest.aspx]', 710, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, 'Cloud - Oct - Nov 2019', '2019-10-03T00:00:00', '2019-11-13T00:00:00', 3, 3, null, null, 'CLP-1288'),
