    ('1835', 'Smith Moore Requirements for renew the subscription of MO', 'Smith Moore鈥檚 renewal is approaching at the end of the year.  They鈥檙e a client that has a $160k spend with us, and we are trying to grow that to $220k over the next two-three years.  They tie feature requests into their renewal conversations, and we can use them to help justify the price increases.  Their two feature requests are as follows:1.       Add a column to the billing information and fee calculation report for whether or not an account is discretionary.  So as not to disrupt other users鈥?workflows, this would ideally be a tick box in the Report Options dialog box to add this column when you generate the report.QB Ticket 1480142.       Create a custodian fee file format for RBC. Smith Moore sent me the specs they鈥檙e using to submit it currently (attached, with comments on what each column means).QB Ticket 148015', -1, 5, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'DOPAMAT-757'),
