    ('2046', 'Morningstar Strategy Universe Entitlement Requirements', 'This ensures that end users will only see strategies and vehicles relevant to their entitlement subscription package.聽聽For the Morningstar Strategy Universe the following entitlement use cases must be met: # Any strategy that is only linked to Custom Funds or Special Pooled Investments (Legal Structures 31 and 51) should not surface. # Any strategy that is only linked to a UBS Separate Account (Legal Structure 52) should not surface. # Any strategy that is linked to both a UBS Separate Account and other vehicles (not custom funds or special pooled investments) should surface. However, a user should not be able to view the UBS Separate Account in the Track Record Analysis component.聽 # Any strategy that is both linked to a Custom Fund or Special Pooled Investment and other vehicles (not a UBS Separate Account) should surface. However, a user should not be able to view the Custom Fund or Special Pooled Investment in Track Record Analysis component.聽 # Any strategy that is only linked to a UBS Separate Account and a Custom Fund or only linked to a UBS Separate Account and a Special Pooled Investment should not surface.聽 # If all the underlying vehicles linked to a strategy move from a public investment to a UBS Separate Account or a Custom Fund or a Special Pooled Investment then the Strategy should be removed from Direct Cloud.聽 # If a strategy in which all the underlying vehicles are Custom Funds, Special Pooled Investments and UBS Separate Accounts is updated and then linked to a public vehicle, that strategy should now surface within products.聽', -1, 2, 5, null, null, null, null, 'Data Services - November-December 2019', '2019-11-06T00:00:00', '2019-12-31T00:00:00', 29, 25, '305', 'Deliver Single Strategy Universe in Web-Based Direct', 'DTCCHI-1121'),
