    ('2071', '[Phase 3 - Part 2 ]  - Existing Peer group Anlaytics through Flink', 'h1. Phase 3Goal : 聽Provide users with ability to perform Peer analytics on rolling timeseries Dp鈥檚 and with unrestricted total number of investments in peer group.聽The first part of this phase is to develop a POC to evaluate performance and costs for a use case with different scenarios. 聽The results of the POC will help determine the tech solution we need to implement.Use case:聽 A user with all rankable dp鈥檚 in columnset containing dynamic cals + Marted dp鈥檚Scenarios # The request to be split and dynamic calc dp鈥檚 will be ranked in Flink and marted dp鈥檚 will be ranked in database and API v2 stiches both responses together and provide to products.聽 # The request will be sent to flink and all Dp鈥檚 (dynamic calc + Marted) will be ranked in flinkUser impact:For existing features:Direct web : * Users will have the ability to rank on large investment lists * Users will be able to apply peer group ranking on rolling timeseries dp鈥檚 * Users in GRID will be able to increase investment list to 5K(from 2k currently) when applying peer analytics.h3. New FeaturesDirect web : NoneRisks:聽聽聽聽聽 Users related : Noneh2. Assumptions * API v2 able to stitch data from async request and flink in one response.聽Timeline:聽 4 months,聽 starting in October 鈥?Mid Feb 2020', -1, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, '229', 'Dynamic Calc and Currency Conversion Migration Out of SQL', 'DTPA-5308'),
