that component. 鈥淲ill Ridout鈥?is our first point of contact from EC team. # Get onboarded with DataAPI teams strategy API which will provide us the underlying model portfolio data. # Onboarding EC Screener component might involve integration with the Strategy API for model data and EAMS systems. Strategy for model data and EAMS for entitlements ( so that we show 200 models instead of 8000 models) # For MVP, we do not need to create real UI components ( corresponding to the donut models from mockups). We can live with the Grid/dropdown 聽based selection ( Just like how Office cloud already has it). Again onboarding EC component will lead us to more on this. 聽If we have time, we could create 鈥榙onut model screens鈥?as *reusable* UI components and make it available for all other teams in M* to use. 聽As of today there is no team that owns this 鈥渢o be developed鈥?UI component. It doesn鈥檛 have a home today. Our discussion leaned on the premise that TRX could own it and possibly hand it over to EC team as EC team owns all other ente', 562, 2, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 34, 34, null, null, 'TRX-3532'),
