    ('2239', 'FIS - IRS Holding Cashflow Analytics', 'This epic is for cashflow analytics calculation of IRS holdings (Portfolio Holding DTID: SI or OS聽)聽https://morningstaronline.sharepoint.com/sites/FICP/Shared%20Documents/Forms/AllItems.aspx?csf=1&e=3cnGzI&RootFolder=%2Fsites%2FFICP%2FShared%20Documents%2FInterest%20Rate%20Swap&FolderCTID=0x01200090453700C7BE5547868348085BC46239Sample Portfolio:MPID 883143  PortfolioDate 2018-3-31.', -1, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 13, 13, null, null, 'FIS-108'),
    ('2240', 'Design for: Transactions Missing Price', 'UX: [https://morningstar.invisionapp.com/share/8TNRPMMMAZW#/316936264_01_Cover]聽Visual spec: [https://morningstar.invisionapp.com/share/ZKKSCODJGQD#/316939084_reviewMissingPrice-Cover]聽----Expanding off of work does in CLP-204.*Issue*: When Back Office Service(BOS) imports my client/account data, it only reconciles (balances) by accounts via shares, not market value or price.聽 This leaves potential for transactions without any price information to get posted to my live client/account data. Missing prices from transactions can聽 impact the return calculations I run on my clients/account so I need to be aware when this happens so that I can go manually add a price to the transaction*Goal*: To allow users to keep tabs on the data BOS imports for them so they can catch anything that may impact the returns they review and share with clients.Currently, BOS team is running this report and uploading it to Client Portal for Cloud users to review.聽 Phase one is about just getting Office Cloud users access to this info within Office Cloud UI so they can reduce they don''t have to worry about tracking data information in multiple locations. (and it will help streamline BOS team''s time). Future phases will add more focus to over process and usability enhancement accross the program.*Dependencies*: OC, DOPA{color:#0747a6}*Example of Report from 3.x*{color}:聽[^Transaction Price Missing Report.xlsx]*Out of Scope:* * Total Redesign of the Review Incoming Data Modal聽 * Adding new features or flows outside of the current Review Incoming Data workflows ** Helping user get to where they can take action is ok, but adding extra features and flagging in other area of Cloud may be out of scope.聽 We have a Phase 2 of Incoming data usability items.聽 We can add additional recommendations surrounding this report to that. * Changing BOS''s process/service/ UIS tool ( this is definitely a longer term item that needs to be looked into)*Unknow