    ('2390', 'Design for Download/Print Multiple Reports', '{color:#d04437}*Problem:*{color}聽Currently, Office Cloud users can only download or print one聽pdf at a time from Reports.聽 The user has to spend a large about of time whenever they want to back up reports for compliance/record keeping needs or printing reports to distribute to clients across their practice.聽*Who is the target?*聽All Office Cloud users聽聽*What are they trying to do?* * Download reports ran on clients to an outside drive or server (example, download all the pdfs ran from a batch).聽 ** ex: many聽firms will have a back up server or something they do for their own compliance practices. * Print multiple reports at one time to distribute across the clients in your practice (remember, many advisors have a large book of retired clients, who are not all comfortable with going electronic to report delivery)聽*What is the scope of the ask?*聽聽Download/Print on multiple pdfs only focusing on聽when that action happens聽within Reports. Other聽areas of OC out of scope.*what are the known dependencies?* Office Cloud squad only聽*what is the AC?*AC1: As an advisor, I would like the ability to download multiple聽pdfs from Reports area at one time.聽-AC2: As an advisor, I would like the ability to聽print multiple聽pdfs from Reports area at one time.-聽 Descoped from current Design/Dev project.聽*What''s the definition of Completed, when is the task done?* * we may need to agree on this some more.聽 What is the max # this action can be taken on at a time?聽聽 * If we determine that we can only solve for AC1 or AC2 , & not both this first phase, that is enough to consider phase 1 complete.*What is the time frame?*聽聽Doc Management is a high priority topic for YE. We would live to dev/deliver this feature by 2018 Year-end or jan 2019*Are there any unknowns?*聽 * -_Technical work it would take to download more than one report at the same time._- * -_What is the # limit of how many pfds they can select at a time to perform this action