    ('2577', 'Research Portal Featured Page Redesign', 'JTBD:聽When I visit the Research Portal''s Featured Page, I want to interact with relevant Morningstar Research so I can make informed decisions about my holdings/portfolios/clients/lists/accounts.聽 聽聽----*Background:* On May 29th 2015 Research Portal''s Featured Page went live. It has been this long since we have made any substantial changes and need design resources for an overhaul.聽We have learned that Videos should be more prominent for the Advisor audience. We are also producing more "Charticle" content for the editor''s picks section that would require more prominence on the page and additional places for images to appear.聽 The MDS team also created a grid layout component we may want to consider implementing. This epic will act as a discovery ticket for the team to get our options together and an estimate of each option.聽', 704, 0, 5, '#069de2', null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'CLP-881'),
    ('2578', 'Show Morningstar Research and Filings for more than one selected investment', 'As a user, I would like to be able to select multiple objects within the platform and view Morningstar Research about them within components for comparison purposes. 聽+User Jobs+ When I''m comparing multiple securities, I want to analyze multiple securities side-by-side so I can choose the single best candidate.When I鈥檓 analyzing a single security, I want to find a handful of peers, similar securities, and/or category average so I can compare and understand how unique the security is (and in what ways).聽', 760, 0, 5, '#a59e89', null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'CLP-449'),
    ('2579', '"Free" Research Portal for Marketing Campaigns', 'As Morningstar Sales and Marketing, I would like to avoid having to set up trial accounts and instead be able to provide prospective clients access to a version of Morningstar Research Portal to entice them buy seats of Cloud.聽The Marketing team currently maintains the Research Blog, launched in 2017 to provide gated research content to prospects.Blog:聽[http://www.morningstar.com/blog]Their schedule is maintained here: [https://morningstaronline-my.sharepoint.com/:x:/g/personal/jaimelyn_aitken_morningstar_com/EVtYs3Z7zD9Dv5oU3CiJy6wBNiggPyBJjBOjPqfsLJFP8A?e=ROJvPt]We want to improve this process by providing a deeper dive for these prospects into the Research Portal Product.聽 聽+User Jobs+ When I prospect for clients, some of them don''t have time nor do they want to provide their information to get set up with a trial account. To reach these future users, I want to provide them with access to Research Portal so they can explore our offering before committing to a contract.UX Mock Flow:聽[https://morningstar.invisionapp.com/share/DAGB1JZXQVG]聽PPT:聽[https://morningstaronline-my.sharepoint.com/:p:/g/personal/jordan_sheckman_morningstar_com/EXHbvSi2bmNOng2MB9X8PrEBEfm3HB0YJIITLXmQs2U7bA?e=l9FKAa]*Background* * Retire (Refresh) the global Corporate Research Library 鈥?The [Corporate site|http://corporate1.morningstar.com/ResearchLibrary/] research library is built off a legacy Ektron content management system that also pulls certain content from the Research Publishing system, RPS. 聽Back in the day. . . before the introduction of the [Morningstar Blog|http://www.morningstar.com/blog], [LinkedIn|https://www.linkedin.com/company/morningstar/], [Twitter|https://twitter.com/MorningstarInc] and the [Facebook social media campaigns|https://www.facebook.com/MorningstarInc/], the Research Library was the primary way for interested parties to access *+some,+* not all of our thought leadership research papers without a pay wall or product to log in to. 聽*Questions/Considerations/Concerns*聽 * Performance - Research Portal on Shared Services server likely won鈥檛 be able to handle the performance load needed to support this traffic. * Paywall - Bypassing Direct Cloud鈥檚 login Paywall and UIM. 聽Jordan mentioned possibly passing a token or some form of authentication for free access to a Research Portal document or set of documents for a free trial session. * Research Distribution Strategy 鈥?We can鈥檛 give all of our research away for free. There will be work required of us to come up with a new edition that runs off of specific content that can be accessed via this design. The current state of the Corporate Research library appears to run off these collections: [http://rps.morningstar.com/api/v2/654566632/collections] when the documents only have these tags on them: Magazine Article, Research Paper, Methodology Document and Factsheet. We鈥檒l need to support more of them, but this is just for reference to understand what鈥檚 being done now. JSON: [http://rps.morningstar.com/', 171, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'CLP-448'),
