    ('2640', 'POC of Fail Fast Plan -auto-scaling of DCS framework Sep-Oct', 'Goal聽 # Validate the approach to leverage auto-scaling capability in AWS for DCS/ADS framework聽 # Validate whether the auto-scaling mechanism in AWS could surface our performance requirements.聽*Impacted* *User Experience:* whether the portfolio data could always be populated in stable performance despite the business cycle (for example, quarter end reporting peak time) or ad hoc event (batch import while onboarding new client)聽聽High-Level Explanation of Solution聽 # We will leverage AWS ECS and auto-scaling technology for DCS/ADS framework聽Out of Scope聽 # Not include the performance testing聽聽Assumption聽 # We will leverage the on-prem 3.x service to retrieve data for this POC聽POC Tasks聽 # Setup DCS framework by using AWS ECS聽 # Design and implement the mechanism to enable auto-scaling for worker/scheduler/fast-CGI when the queue size reaches the threshold.聽聽 # Implement the auto scaling logic for workers聽 # When the # of workers is changed, we need a mechanism to change the # of scheduler and fast-CGI instances accordingly. Because we need to keep the ratio between them (We need to figure out the ratio based on our current on-prem deployment).聽 # When a new scheduler is created, we need a mechanism to notice the workers/fast-CGI. Similarly, when shutdown a scheduler the workers/fast-CGI also need to be noticed. (Currently we put the list of schedulers in the config file of each worker/fast-CGI, should we use a centralized DB to maintain this list?)聽聽Test Cases聽 # Case 1:聽 calculate one case on ADS on AWS and match current ADS result聽 # Case 2:聽聽 when the queue size reaches the threshold, the ECS (worker/scheduler/fast-CGI) can be auto scaled.聽聽Risks聽 # The scaling mechanism in AWS might not meet our requirement on worker scaling, like it may take longer time to load new instance than we expected.聽Expected Results (Measure of Success)聽 # DCS framework was established on AWS with ECS聽 # Worker can be automatic scaled and shutdown聽聽 # Scheduler/fast-CGI can be automatic scaled and shutdown聽Resource & Estimation聽 # Leaders: Xiaoshuang Sun聽 # Working Team: Rocky Li, Andy Wei, Shixin Deng, Frank Wen聽 # Estimation: 6 weeks (11 weeks Man Hour)聽', -1, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, 'Data Services - August-September 2019', '2019-08-14T00:00:00', '2019-09-24T00:00:00', 0, 0, null, null, 'DOPCSTA-4815'),
