    ('2874', 'PPI-4659 New Liquidity Tools Part II', 'Bsiness case:Liquidity considerations are key when evaluating asset managers, investment strategies, and alpha potential, so it''s imperitive that we develop better tools around this. The liquidity tool protoype and resulting research paper have also received good feedback and interest from investors and clients.Benefit:New metrics--e.g., days to liquiditate, burndown rate--give investors a more comprehensive view of the capacity and liquidity risk they face, which is key to evaluating a strategy''s ability to generate alpha.Description:Project to productize the liquidity tool prototype created by data/methodology and manager research. Example of prototype''s output is included in the htm file, as is the research paper that uses the new metrics.聽', -1, 2, 5, '#6EBDAB', null, null, null, 'Data Services - November-December 2019', '2019-11-06T00:00:00', '2019-12-31T00:00:00', 30, 19, '253', 'New Liquidity Tools PPI-4659', 'DTCMER-278'),
