    ('3349', '[MPA] RJ Plan Summary Report', '_Description_:聽聽Excel report that contains list of all聽plans in the Raymond James 3(38) program across all providers.聽The report will include the results of the compliance check, along with other plan details like start/end dates.聽聽聽_Delivery__:_聽 * Schedule:聽Morningstar will聽send聽this report to Raymond James three (3)聽times a week 鈥撀爋n Mondays, Wednesdays聽and Fridays, excluding holidays.聽聽 * Format:聽File will be in .xls聽format.聽 * Location:聽Report will be delivered to聽[IFSPartnerReporting@RaymondJames.com|mailto:IFSPartnerReporting@RaymondJames.com]聽聽聽聽聽聽_Data points:_聽Client聽Name聽鈥?this is the Morningstar鈥檚 name for the provider聽聽Provider Plan ID聽鈥?the plan ID as sent in the provider鈥檚 plan list/eligible plans file聽聽Plan Name聽鈥?the plan name聽as sent in the provider鈥檚 plan list/eligible plans file.聽Product ID聽鈥?this is the value Morningstar聽creates for each provider鈥檚 products聽Start Date聽鈥?start date as sent in the provider鈥檚 plan list/eligible plans file.聽End Date聽鈥?end date as sent in the provider鈥檚 plan list/eligible plans file聽or as provided by Raymond James. The first end date received will be retained in the system.聽Plan Status聽鈥?results of the compliance聽process.聽 Will be one of the following values:聽 * Approved 鈥?the plan has met all asset class rules and compliance checks聽 * InFailure 鈥?a plan that was once approved but is no longer in compliance. The plan needs to update the lineup to get back to Approved status聽 * Failed 鈥?a plan that started in a non-approved state by failing the compliance checks. This plan is not considered enrolled in the service. The plan needs to update the lineup to get to an Approved status聽 * Cancelled 鈥?a plan that has voluntarily opted out of the Program.聽Error Code聽鈥?corresponds to error validation document codes聽Error Description聽鈥?explanation of what is wrong with the plan and causing it to have compliance failures聽Deadline Date聽鈥?date by which the plan must correct the issue. Each error聽code聽has its own deadline date.聽聽_Operational_聽_Notes__:_聽Morningstar will generate this report three times a week.聽 The information pulled into the report will be the most recent plans status information across all providers.聽聽聽All聽Raymond James plans聽will be listed in the report, even those in Cancelled status.聽Once a plan is in Cancelled status, it will no longer be included in the compliance process unless it is reinstated with the 3(38) service.聽聽If a provider has indicated that a plan has opted out of the 3(38) service, Morningstar will populate the End Date column with the date based on the plan information received from the provider.聽聽If a plan聽exists in Morningstar鈥檚 database but does not have any associated contact information, there will be an error code = 999 to alert Raymond James of the missing contact details.聽', -1, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'WFIS-51'),
