    ('3388', '2.0 Ownership Lens', 'This will generate a list of fundamental, ownership-based variables that will then be fed into the fundamental factor exposure construction API referenced in RISK-488.聽First, user specifies a FundUniverseId object:FundUniverse = (Name = "Global Equity",Id = "ABC789",LegalStructure = (08, 22, 23, ... )IncludeActive = TRUE,IncludePassive = FALSE,Domicile = (USA, CAN, ...) # default is AllGlobalAssetClassId = (EQ, ALLOC, ...) # default is EquityIncludeFoF = FALSE )聽聽Then, we run a job that takes FundUniverseObject as input to calculate fundamental, ownership-based factors:OwnershipLens(fundUniverse = "ABC789",StartDate = "1-1-2003",holdingsBased = TRUEtradingBased = FALSEweightingScheme = (VWAP, WYZ, Pastor, None)VariableList = ([name = "alpha", id = "alphaId"]...[name = "drawdown", id=drawdownid"])portfolioLookBack = (monthly, quarterly, semi-annual, annual))聽+*Default Options:*+fundUniverse(LegalStructure =( ''08'',''09'',''22'',''23'',''35'',''36'',''37'',''38'',''39'',''40'',''41'',''46'')IncludeActive = TRUE,IncludePassive = FALSE,Domicile = AllGlobalAssetClassId = ''$BCG$EQUTY'' # equity asset classIncludeFoF = FALSE聽)ownershipLens(StartDate =聽"1-1-2003"holdingsBased = TRUEtradingBased = FALSEweightingScheme = NoneportfolioLookBack = quarterly聽)+*Input聽Data:*+聽Input data for Stock ownership calculations:||Date||MasterPotfolioId||HoldingId||Weight||Variable|||2012-01-31|129823|E0USA0105T|27.9|1.1||2012-01-31|129823|E0USA00DBM|12.5|-0.3||2011-12-31|46|F000000G7M|7.2|0.6|Input data for fund ownership calculations:Stock quality is the output from the stock ownership calculation聽||Date||MasterPortfolioID||HoldingId||Weight||StockQuality|||2012-01-31|129823|E0USA0105T|.94|2.06||2012-01-31|129823|E0USA00DBM|1.45|1.68|聽聽*+Output Information:+*聽Note: There should be two output tables. One with Fund information, another with Holding information.聽*Output Fund:*聽||VariableId||Date||MasterPortfolioId||Measure||Weighting||Quality||NumSecurit