    ('3408', '2.0 Model Estimation', 'As a risk model user, I want to be able to see a rich collection of portfolio statistics.聽 This epic implements a mapping from a portfolio to that collection of statistics.For each date, given a collection of premia and residuals we can construct a mechanism to provide forecast statistics.聽 The list of statistics we want to produce are: * variance/volatility * skewness * kurtosis * CVar * Var * Prob Neg ReturnFurthermore market volatility exhibits clustering and mean reversion - so if we are in a period of high volatilty, our expected volatility is high over a short time horizon, but lower over a longer time horizon.聽 So the time horizon for the forecast is an essential input.聽 The horizon can vary from 1 to around 1000 timesteps.The input portfolio can be long and short.聽*Implementation Notes*There is a sketch of an appropriate/suggested way to implement this in the SimpleForecastModel class.聽 There are several actors here: * ForecastModel: maps a portfolio to the collection of forecast statistics.聽 Constructed from a single comovement model, and a collection of residuals models, one residual model fro each security in the universe.聽 This implements the various forecast statistics. * ResidualModel: describes just the residuals from the cross sectional regression.聽 There is one residual model per time period and per security (stock).聽 In implemementation, this should essentially perform ML estimation on one collection of residuals.聽 This can then output the moments for the residuals. * ComovementModel:聽 this describes the comovement of the factors.聽 This should perform ICA on the factors, and then use ML to estimate the model for the signals.聽 This provides a mapping from portfolio factor weights to the moments. * ML to find a GARGH-NIG model for a timeseries.聽 It''s clear that this is a key component for both Residual and Component model, this should be its own function/object as appropriate.*Acceptance Criteria*This is essentially a model which is discovering latent model parameters from real world data.聽 The primary method of model testing is therefore simulating data from known parameters, and testing whether the model can reproduce these parameters.聽 For all statistics, there should be a test showing the statistic can be constructed.So for each statistic, artificial data must be constructed from a probability distribution parameterized by a known statistics.聽 Then the model must be constructed which analyses the data, and the model must reconstruct those statistics just from the artificial data.Time - the forecast methods may sit in the middle of an optimizer for portfolio optimization tasks.聽 They will need to support around 20 calls/second for portfolios of around 500 securities.*Other Notes*GARCH models require several hundred samples to produce good parameter estimates - so the testing strategy and code must explicitly address this.The mean forecast for the factors in the comovement model should be able to be specified using a variety of ', -1, 2, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 34, 0, null, null, 'RISK-521'),
