    ('3727', 'Design for: Office Cloud Digital Account Opening - Schwab', 'h3. *Issue:* Advisors are looking for more single workflow solutions between the various pieces of technology they use to between their daily tasks.聽 Since many advisor workflows can touch many products, advisors are looking for a way to better connect those products and make for easier workflows.h3. {color:#ff0000}*Goal:* {color}To provide advisors who custody with Schwab, an easy/seamless way start the process of opening a new account directly from Office Cloud.{color:#ff0000}*Why this now?* {color}Digital account opening is already a service provided by all of our major competitors. Although in its initial state, it might not feel like a giant value add right away, it is critical to get a solution started in Office.聽 We need to show our users that we are listen to market needs, and are making steps into providing expanded cross product workflows. This first step is to show good face to our users and future prospects.h3. *Dependencies*: OC, Design, TRXDev Epic: CLP-1320*Blain''s Intial Document:*聽 [https://morningstaronline-my.sharepoint.com/:w:/g/personal/blain_hefty_morningstar_com/ETSQYWFvoL9PvWFZOklYq-UBOJeYv60jObk6qCs_qcgtZw?e=2388ih]This is the first of a multi-phase experience.聽 The as the api availability expands, there will be more room for additional interactions: * Phase 1: Account Owner name Only * Phase 2: We will send Address, email, phone via聽Schwab Contacts API.聽 * Phase 2/3:聽Status Alerts via Schwab Alerts API.聽h3. *Out of Scope:*聽 * Redesign on Integrations page * Opening more than one account at a time * passing Schwab any data point beyond Account Owner name and Advisor Master Account * The ability to track new account opening status within Office Cloud * changes to steps that happen in Schwab UIh3. {color:#ff0000}*Syncing Office Cloud & Schwab OpenView**:*{color}*(Screen shots are from TRX integration聽with Schwab)*1. Initiate sync from Office Cloud聽2. From Cloud UI, enter following information: # Schwab Advisor Center User Name # Password!image-2019-11-04-15-21-14-590.png|width=670,height=249!3. Save entered data to Office!image-2019-11-04-15-22-40-720.png|width=656,height=274!4. Once info is saved, login to Schwab Advisor Center> Window opens on Schwab side with User Agreement.!image-2019-11-04-15-23-07-488.png|width=678,height=364!聽h3. {color:#ff0000}*Launching Account Opening Steps:*聽{color}*From Office UI -->* * Establish digital account opening functionality for custodian Schwab within Office Cloude * From within Office Cloud Advisor clicks "Open Charles Schwab Account"*Passes to Schwab UI-->* * Advisor selects their Client the Schwab Master Account, which will be used to create the new Client Schwab client Account. The Master Account is Schwab''s numerical identifier for the Advisor. * Advisor selects the Account type they wish to open. * Advisor selects a current client or creates a new client whose contact information will be used to open new account. * Advisor confirms client and client account details prior to submi', 391, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, 'Cloud - Nov-Dec 2019', '2019-11-14T00:00:00', '2019-12-25T00:00:00', 6, 0, '264', 'Office Cloud - Digital Account Opening', 'OC-5273'),
