    ('3844', '[MPA] UBS - Plan Dashboard', 'We will modify the current fields within the plan dashboard as outlined in the table below. 聽|Current Name|UBS Preferred Name||Fund Health|Fund Status||Healthy|Approved Funds||On Watch|On Watch Funds||Removed|Unapproved Funds|聽UBS has indicated that they would like dollar amounts included next to the percentages in the active lineup assets chart. Morningstar would sum fund balances at the broad asset class level.We will need to develop a new process to handle plans that are live on MPA in which the advisor has changed the provider outside of MPA. There will be period where the plan will be in a live state on the advisor鈥檚 dashboard with one provider and a 鈥渂uild lineup status鈥?with another provider. For now, we would list the plan twice and then remove the old listing once the plan is live with its new provider. UBS confirmed that this is OK.', -1, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'WFIS-78'),
