    ('4062', 'Convert Dazl to BAA', '*Background*:Dazl is making changed to their File Layout and File Delivery Instead of updating existing EDM Dazl interface, we will start using BAA to bring in this data. We need to convert Sigma/Sammons/Founder DAZl data to the new Sigma/Sammons/Founder BAA interface. *Requirements:*1. CIS-5007/CIS-5265 Convert existing Founder/Sigma/Sammons DAZL data to BAA, also need to remove Fund Code for existing Founder BAA data !Data Points.png|thumbnail! 2. CIS-5263/CIS-5264  Map Custodian Name to FI ID  !FI ID to Custodian.png|thumbnail! 3.  CIS-5277/CIS-5278  prase FI_Supplied_Firm_ID and Store it as Fund Code     a. Add FI ID column in Account/Transaction/Position/Reconciliaiton blotter        Currently FI ID is saved as Fund code and BOS users use it to filter data, so we need to add a new data         column ''FI ID'' in blotter to diplay it     b. prase the new data points and store it as Fund Code4.  CIS-5299  Store Investment Company as FINANCIAL_INSTITUTION_NAME+ FI_Supplied_Firm_ID     a.  store FINANCIAL_INSTITUTION_NAME as FI Name     b. Add FI Name (display Investment Company) Column in Account/Transaction/Position/Reconciliaiton blotter     c. store Investment Company as FINANCIAL_INSTITUTION_NAME+ FI_Supplied_Firm_ID !screenshot-2.png|thumbnail!    4. Identify the same account by Account Number+ Fund Code+ FI ID - {color:#FF8B00}No need to do any changes{color}Currently, we Use Custodian ID + Account Number to identify the same account, and set different rule to generate Custodian ID per Custodians. Such as     For DAZL, it has one custodian ID only     For DST, its custodian ID is different from Fund Code', -1, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 11, 0, null, null, 'CIS-5335'),
    ('4063', 'Moneny Market Price', 'This example is a unique money market in a charitable giving Fidelity account but needs to be investigated/resolved for all UIS imports. UIS defaults the price to $1.00 when the type is 鈥渕oney market fund鈥?and disregards the imported price. In order for the correct price to be imported we had to change the security type to "Other" and then UIS will pull in the correct imported price of $15.77.If there is a Price in the data file for a Money Market we need the system to be able to read the price in the file and not automatically import a 1.00 price.An additional document and files are located in the following folder: Y:\AWSOE\Unified Import Testing\Tickets Submitted\BOS-35*Please see comments on BOS-35', -1, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'CIS-5135'),
