    ('4070', 'UIS splunk installation', '# install splunk in UIS workstation, webserver # figure out how to get log from OE # get the following statistic information (IntefaceId, Start Date,聽End Date,聽Number of accounts,聽Number of transactions,聽Number of OOBs,聽Job status (fail or success),SessionId (option))To-do List: * *Make the log file follow the聽[Application Logging Standard|https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/technology/Application+Logging+Standard]*聽 * *Submit a service desk ticket to install Splunk Agent*聽(called聽*SplunkForwarder*) in the application server. This generally will take about 2-3 business days. * *Fill the request form for Splunk logging*. Here is the entrance聽[Splunk Requesting Splunk Services|https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/GITI/Splunk+Requesting+Splunk+Services]. Click link "[Create a new request|https://mswiki.morningstar.com/pages/createpage-entervariables.action?spaceKey=GIR&templateId=54067201&fromPageId=53642173]"聽then you will see a request form template. Send the request form to Peter Saine ** Official sample:聽[Splunk Request Form - Sample|https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/GITI/Splunk+Request+Form+-+Sample] ** Go to聽[Splunk Requesting Splunk Services|https://mswiki.morningstar.com/display/GITI/Splunk+Requesting+Splunk+Services]聽for more detail information if there is questions', -1, 0, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'CIS-4304'),
    ('4071', 'UIS Auto Generate Adjustment', '聽After doing a Side by Side with BOS DMA when import BAA data聽The biggest issue I seen was with how BOS handles adding Adjustment鈥︹€︹€︹€︹€︹€︹€︹€?聽Current Work Flow聽BOS will come across a Case were adjusting transactions must be added to an account聽The cases are Noted in there tracking system, BOSDB聽Then EACH DAY, they manually sort through the Reconciliation errors to find the Noted cases and add the needed Transactions聽Each team member spends around or over 2 hours a day on this process聽In most cases, they are not reviewing the adjustment they adding, just looking at the Name of the holding, recognizing it as one that can be adjusted and adding the transactions聽聽Reviewing the adjustment transactions is part of their QA process聽聽鈥︹€︹€︹€︹€︹€︹€︹€?聽Because we Know there will be cases were adjustment transaction will be needed.聽We should find a way for Import to systemically add them聽This will BOS team the Time of putting them in and help to avoid human error聽We should also build in adjustment threshold, to limit what it adjusted without review聽聽鈥︹€︹€︹€︹€︹€︹€︹€?BAA will get the most use from the tool, BUT would be good to have it open to all interfaces聽聽', -1, 2, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 0, 0, null, null, 'CIS-4267'),
