    ('4080', 'Performance Issues with Large Volume DST Import', 'BOS is experiencing severe performance issues when trying to get DST data imported for a new customer (Harbour).聽 Loading the blotter, posting data and running reconciliation takes an extremely long period of time, or sometimes it will time out and not finish.聽 The DST import includes聽128 fund companies with 70,765 accounts.聽 The imports cannot be completed consistently in current state, so we''d like to understand the root cause and what we may be able to do to improve performance significantly.BOS has tried breaking up the import into smaller chunks, but this really isn''t a solution either.聽Here''s an example of what BOS runs into:聽 the import was once kicked off at 4:30am ET, and after lunch the import timed out and didn''t finish.Login used:聽 [newaccounts4.oemanager@morningstar.com|mailto:newaccounts4.oemanager@morningstar.com]Customer''s Info:聽Harbour Investments Inc (4672415)  Office Login: ahellenbrand@harbourinv.com聽', -1, 2, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 3, 0, null, null, 'CIS-3806'),
